# Worker Agent Service — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

**Layer 8 — Parallel Worker Agent Layer** for HelioX RAG 3.0, per architecture blueprint §2.8. Each worker processes a single chunk against the locked SQO, extracting citation-bound claims.

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD
    SQO["Locked SQO"] --> POOL["WorkerPool"]
    RET["Retrieved Chunks (K)"] --> POOL
    POOL --> W1["Worker 1"]
    POOL --> W2["Worker 2"]
    POOL --> WK["Worker K"]
    W1 --> |"LLM Call"| O1["WorkerOutput"]
    W2 --> |"LLM Call"| O2["WorkerOutput"]
    WK --> |"LLM Call"| OK["WorkerOutput"]
    O1 --> AGG["Aggregation"]
    O2 --> AGG
    OK --> AGG
    AGG --> CHECK{"avg confidence ≥ 0.90?"}
    CHECK -->|"Yes"| STOP["Early Stop + Cancel"]
    CHECK -->|"No"| WAIT["Wait for more"]
    STOP --> RESULT["PoolResult"]
    WAIT --> RESULT
```

