## Worker Output Schema (§2.8)

```json
{
  "worker_id": "uuid",
  "chunk_id": "uuid",
  "claim": "Factual statement derived from chunk",
  "supporting_spans": [
    {"start": 142, "end": 387, "text": "exact quoted span"}
  ],
  "reasoning_trace": "Step-by-step reasoning path",
  "confidence_local": 0.88,
  "coverage_score": 0.45,
  "status": "SUFFICIENT | INSUFFICIENT"
}
```

## Cost Control Mechanisms

| Mechanism | Source | Implementation |
|-----------|--------|---------------|
| Token budget split | §9.1 | 19,200 total ÷ K workers |
| Early stopping | §7.2 | Cancel remaining when avg confidence ≥ 0.90 |
| Max workers cap | §2.2 | Never more than 12 concurrent workers |
| Pool timeout | §8.5 | 15s soft wall, partial results on breach |
| Worker retry | §8.2 | 1 retry on failure, re-dispatch same chunk |

